data.description: This beautiful 4 bed, 3.5 bath home boasts on an oversized lot in Castlegate 1.Walk into perfection in this sleek and spacious floor plan! With a formal study, open kitchen layout, and living room that flow together seamlessly, this floor plan is sure to please all! Once inside, you will be wowed by the spacious and thoughtful layout, a large utility room, and all of the natural light let in by the windows in the breakfast nook and living room. Also on the main floor is an oversized primary bedroom suite with a walk-in closet that dreams are made of. Featuring a powder room on the first floor, your guests will enjoy their privacy without having to use a shared bathroom. Upstairs, you will find spacious secondary bedrooms, secondary bathrooms, and a huge game room that your family will love.
